trans-unit.source: Provides for compilation and caching of queries for reuse.
Conceptually this class contains a single method (`Compile`) with several overloads.
You call the <xref:System.Data.Linq.CompiledQuery.Compile%2A> method to create a new delegate to represent the compiled query.
Compilation does not occur until the first time the query is executed.
Compiles the query.
